{"time": 1768301766921, "blocks": [{"id": "initial", "data": {"text": "Technology utilization in warehouse operations:"}, "type": "paragraph"}, {"id": "iZQ7Vki-ke", "data": {"meta": {"counterType": "numeric"}, "items": [{"meta": {}, "items": [], "content": "Warehouse Management Systems (WMS) - automates inventory tracking, order processing, and storage allocation"}, {"meta": {}, "items": [], "content": "Barcode scanning - enables quick and accurate identification of goods and reduces manual errors"}, {"meta": {}, "items": [], "content": "Radio Frequency Identification (RFID) - provides real-time tracking of inventory movement"}, {"meta": {}, "items": [], "content": "Automated Storage and Retrieval Systems (AS/RS) - improves storage density and retrieval speed"}, {"meta": {}, "items": [], "content": "Robotics and automated guided vehicles (AGVs) - handles material movement and reduces labor costs"}, {"meta": {}, "items": [], "content": "Inventory management software - monitors stock levels, reorder points, and forecasts demand"}, {"meta": {}, "items": [], "content": "Cloud-based systems - enables real-time data access and collaboration across locations"}, {"meta": {}, "items": [], "content": "Pick-to-light and put-to-light systems - guides workers to correct locations and improves picking accuracy"}, {"meta": {}, "items": [], "content": "Mobile devices and tablets - allows workers to access information and update systems on the go"}, {"meta": {}, "items": [], "content": "Data analytics and reporting tools - provides insights for decision-making and process improvement"}], "style": "ordered"}, "type": "list"}]}	019bb6ff-aabc-7176-b636-2a23815cf5f8	2026-01-14 21:35:06.055827	2026-01-13 10:56:07.356177	0	0	t	f	01986e2a-aa36-7386-9bdf-ab2aff6ac71e	\N	019bb6d2-3753-7781-a6fd-e65cc42c1ba6
