cation opportunities closer to home for many students.	Ministry of Education	["TVC", "College", "Technical", "Vocational"]	01986e39-dfc8-78b6-b441-5f29c92142ed	2025-10-06 14:51:29.59202	2025-08-03 04:39:03.368729	\N	01986e2a-aa36-7386-9bdf-ab2aff6ac71e	tharaka-technical-and-vocational-college
