g meaningful contributions in their respective fields.	Ministry of Education	["National", "Polytechnic"]	01986e39-fba8-70ff-af53-91d2abc94d54	2025-10-06 14:51:29.592024	2025-08-03 04:39:10.504381	\N	01986e2a-aa36-7386-9bdf-ab2aff6ac71e	the-bungoma-national-polytechnic
